      "text": [
        "112 - وَقَالَ أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «إِنَّ أَفْوَاهَكُمْ طُرُقُ اَلْقُرْآنِ فَطَهِّرُوهَا بِالسِّوَاكِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.112 - The Commander of the Faithful Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\n\"Your mouths are the pathways of the Quran, so purify them with siwak (toothstick).\""
        ]
      }
    }
